{"tid":456093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CIA ：拉登電腦有龍珠、銀魂、火影忍者、FF7盜版遊戲動畫","createTime":"2017-11-02T16:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T04:18:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5c9a72303e1979d96c905d6ac2e6aee733ad44","tid":456093,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"被認定為國際恐佈組織阿爾蓋達的領導人之一賓‧拉登，在 2011 年被美軍殺害，當時在他的隱藏之處內尋獲的電腦，交予 CIA 美國中央情報局進行深入調查。而在本日（香港時間11月2日）凌晨 CIA 在網路上公開這部電腦內容量321GB 的共 47 萬個檔案，當中發現拉登電腦有《Final Fantasy VII》、《龍珠》、《銀魂》、《火影忍者》的盜版遊戲與動畫、《New Super Mario Bros》等 DS 盜版遊戲、《Resident Evil》（Bio Hazard）盜版電影。<br />\n<br />\n美國中央情報局 CIA 在香港時間今日（11月2日）凌晨公開拉登電腦共 321GB 檔案予公眾下載。當中涉及侵犯版權的檔案、有關於美軍情報的檔案已經被過濾，但 CIA 公佈了這些檔案的內容列表。有些檔案頗為有趣，雖然未知是否拉登本人享用，但肯定他或者他的助手曾經享用過有關內容。<br />\n<br />\nNDS 遊戲：New Super Mario Bros、Animal Crossing<br />\n<br />\n電子遊戲：Final Fantasy VII、Army Men 2、Zuma<br />\n<br />\n電影：Resident Evil、Batman Gotham Knight、Antz、Cars、Chicken Little、Ice Age：Dawn of the Dinosaurs<br />\n<br />\n動畫影片：Naruto、Bleach、Dragon Ball、Storm Rider &ndash; Clash of the Evils、Devil May Cry<br />\n<br />\n除了以上的電子遊戲、電影之外，拉登亦搜集了不少 CNN、National Geographic 的紀錄片。我們很難想像拉登會玩 Animal Crossing 這款生活型村莊遊戲。當然這些檔案只是在他的電腦發現，未知是否真正接觸過。另外早前有消息報道，拉登電腦內存有不少色情內容，但在今次公開的檔案清單中就未有發現。<br />\n<br />\nCIA 因不明原因暫中止公開<br />\n除了以上娛樂專用內容外，CIA 當然也尋獲不少阿爾蓋達組織的記錄。例如 有1.8萬個資料檔案、7.9萬件聲音與相片檔案、拉登本人演說的錄音與錄影、拉登與家人拍攝的家庭影片。<br />\n<br />\n中央情報局原本把所有檔案（除侵犯版權與美軍機密檔案外）全部公開。但由於「技術問題」在本文截稿時（11月2日下午）官方暫停了公開檔案，所有連結都變成失效。CIA 早前指出檔案雖然經詳細審查，但亦可能會有 malware 等有害程式潛伏於檔案中，要求下載人士注意。<br />\n<br />\nCIA 有關於今次事件的官方網站：<a href=\"https://www.cia.gov/news-information/press-releases-statements/2017-press-releases-statements/cia-releases-additional-files-recovered-in-ubl-compound-raid.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Fnews-information%2Fpress-releases-statements%2F2017-press-releases-statements%2Fcia-releases-additional-files-recovered-in-ubl-compound-raid.html&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=685acf03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cia.gov/news-information/press-releases-statements/2017-press-releases-statements/cia-releases-additional-files-recovered-in-ubl-compound-raid.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ef4fc6cb287fcba0da36eb7dc3e29a094976ea7","tid":456093,"uid":36178,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"無av打死我都唔信<br />\nbtw FF7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e359a09cd3b239103bec2c935281b5374bd67239","tid":456093,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"再一次證明所以組織只係為左利益, 並冇什麼偉大嘅理想,一切都只係口號"},{"pid":"71d8acaf1196b5a984629f14e0352b048705c13a","tid":456093,"uid":48210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T21:24:33.000Z","msg":"想像唔到拉登玩 animal crossing"},{"pid":"9f55c267d89be92ab467b38032e862e20b4f41e4","tid":456093,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T21:32:52.000Z","msg":"毒撚mode"},{"pid":"6246b01432787f10349a4ed33953e942a80d657a","tid":456093,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T21:34:37.000Z","msg":"拉登睇ice age嗰陣究竟諗緊咩<br />\n<br />\n屌諗起iron man 3嗰條撚屌mandarin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797e1464868e18c8a62bcb131501b18cc0400618","tid":456093,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T21:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4889f77622a30299b7e098a11d25b13bd417a56c","tid":456093,"uid":49955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T21:41:53.000Z","msg":"登仔係咪好同情曉？"},{"pid":"bee56544bab11b00984a2326e7afb473f0b94f9c","tid":456093,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T22:36:00.000Z","msg":"完全估佢唔到會玩animal crossing同ff7<img src=\"/